'The Real' Host Jeannie Mai On Fighting Human Trafficking 
Mai’s work helping victims has grown over the years as the business of sex trafficking continues to expand.

data.description: Jeannie Mai, host of The Real talk show shares her work with helping human trafficking victims on their path to recovery and what you can do to put an end to the business of selling humans. #IfIOnlyKnew
data.title: 'The Real' Host Jeannie Mai On Fighting Human Trafficking
